Create and manage recurring rule templates, then expand them into concrete events.

Examples:
  pomo event recur add --title "Weekly Review" --start 2026-03-02T09:00 --duration 1h --freq weekly --byday MO,WE --domain Planning --subtopic General
  pomo event recur list --active-only
  pomo event recur edit 1 --interval 2 --title "Deep Review"
  pomo event recur expand --from 2026-03-01T00:00 --to 2026-03-31T23:59

Usage:
  pomo event recur [command]

Available Commands:
  add         add a recurring rule
  delete      delete a recurring rule
  edit        edit a recurring rule
  expand      generate recurring occurrences into events in a date window
  list        list recurring rules

Flags:
  -h, --help   help for recur

Use "pomo event recur [command] --help" for more information about a command.
